item, include concrete steps and commands (or links to runbooks).

### Config changes
- [ ] Required / Not required
- Files or keys:
- Steps and commands:

### Fabric schema changes
- [ ] Required / Not required
- Schema or artifact:
- Steps and commands:

### Database changes
- [ ] Required / Not required
- Migrations, indexes, backfill:
- Steps and commands:

### Redis changes
- [ ] Required / Not required
- Keys, TTL, data structure:
- Steps and commands:

### Deploy order
- Prerequisites before app deploy:
- Safe rollback notes:

## 2. Changes summary

### Feature overview
- What changed and why (2–4 sentences).

### SDD
- Path: `docs/sdd/<feature-slug>.md`
- Phases delivered in this PR:
- Open questions or follow-ups:

### ADRs
- [ ] No new or updated ADRs
- Related ADRs (link paths under `docs/adr/`):
